<p class="caption"><em>Pixel 3.</em></p>
</div></div>
<p id="a8k2zJ">Finally, you’re getting a 16-megapixel selfie camera on the OnePlus 8, same as the 8 Pro. Aside from a touch of skin smoothing and brightening, both do a good job. (I promise we’re done with pictures of my face now. Trust me, reviewing a smartphone camera while social distancing is a bit of a challenge.)</p>
